  * source/vm/hvm.c
    * hb_itemMove() function added, which is intended for use instead of
      the 
        hb_itemCopy( pDest,pSource )
        hb_itemClear( pSource )
      This allows to speed up some internal vm functions.
      The idea was borrowed from xHarbour.

